rket reforms he implemented in the past seven years, and make France a less attractive country for foreign investors.\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9863500835439063, \"rank\": 0.013803940451775455, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his electoral campaign\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"his far-right\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"the far-left opponents\", \"from\": 1052, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"the pro-market reforms\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the past seven years\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1168}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign investors\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With theOlympic Gamesofficially kicking off on Friday with anunprecedented opening ceremony on the Seine, around a hundred of heads of state and government as well as top executives from the world's business elite will be mingling in Paris.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1335, \"end\": 1340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999540550420867, \"rank\": 4.5944504570207846e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995100097, \"rank\": 4.900759744708504e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Gamesofficially\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"anunprecedented opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1327}, {\"ngram\": \"heads\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"state\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"government\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"top executives\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's business elite\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite a disastrously negative trade balance for goods, under Macron France proved particularly strongin attractingforeign money, thanks in part to generous subsidies.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2420873135932435e-23, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9863500835439063, \"rank\": 0.013803940451775455, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a disastrously negative trade balance\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"goods\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"particularly strongin attractingforeign money\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"generous subsidies\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While many of the executives attending the lunch already invested in France, Musk's Tesla has no factories in France,despite Macron's effortsto convince him.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbp